                "className": "mord mathcal",
                "style": {
                  "marginRight": "0.05834em"
                }
              }}>{`C`}</span></span></span></span></span>{` to compute accurate expectation values with respect to `}<span parentName="p" {...{
        "className": "katex"
      }}><span parentName="span" {...{
          "className": "katex-mathml"
        }}><math parentName="span" {...{
